# Readme

This image allows deploying a [vouch](https://github.com/vouch/vouch-proxy) instance.
The OAUTH_CLIENT_ID and OAUTH_CLIENT_SECRET variables are set by fetching `nu-secrets`.
To determine where to fetch the secrets set `OAUTH_CLIENT_ID_S3_LOCATION` and `OAUTH_CLIENT_SECRET_S3_LOCATION` with the appropriate s3 path (e.g. `s3://nu-secrets-br-prod/marquez/oauth_client_id`).
Any other setup must be done via environment variables, to find list of variables [see](https://github.com/vouch/vouch-proxy#configuring-via-environmental-variables).